==Forces==
Please see the June 2016 version of this article. The Forces section shows that the contributions of the Allies were Austria (3,700), Württemberg (2,000) and Prussia (800). But the vast majority of the 26,400 Allied cavalry were Russians. [[User:Djmaschek|Djmaschek]] ([[User talk:Djmaschek|talk]]) 15:32, 8 June 2016 (UTC)
